data.description: Look no further for the perfect home that is meticulously maintained, with an excellent curb appeal. Welcome to The Farms community. Just minutes away from I-85, UNCC, and Uptown Charlotte, this convenient location is for you. Enjoy the spacious 4 bedroom, 2 ½ bath, open floor plan that holds over 2,050 sq. ft of living space. The main floor hosts the Primary bedroom featuring an en-suite bathroom with a walk-in shower, comfortable garden tub, and a generous walk-in closet. The main floor also contains a sizable living room connected to the kitchen, perfect for entertaining guests. Located upstairs are 3 more spacious bedrooms along with a full bathroom. Enjoy quiet evenings in the extensive backyard, with ample room as another entertainment space.
